HEADWORD: Pontifician
<hw>Pon`ti*fi"cian</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who adheres to the pope
or papacy; a papist.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bp.
Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
